Name: Corpse disaster-survivors
About the game: In another failed invasion plan you were caught in a storm Cut off contact with friends who have worked together for many years The city was thrown into a mess by the explosion of the laboratory and the spread of the virus You are blocked by many virus-infected creatures and enemies You don’t know that you are the one who planned this conspiracy The current game is already a reset version Because the game is a work driven out by the author in advance I haven’t finished the optimization yet. If the configuration is not high, friends can wait I will update the game content and optimize patches I wish you all a happy play! (The author is still learning the knowledge of ue4 to makegames.
